Title: Network interface and switch port discovery parameters
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: checks
Date: 1614892941
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.1.0b1

There was a bug in the ruleset "Network interface and switch port
discovery" which prevented users from saving rules without configuring
the discovery of single interfaces (i.e. rules which only change the
grouping behaviour). This has been fixed.
